{"tid":1788732,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人一諗到個ex就覺得噁心","createTime":"2019-12-19T02:10:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T18:53:07.000Z","uid":295958,"like":157,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"db2920736c047479d4ec920a5109aa2c18a175ca","tid":1788732,"uid":295958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:10:56.000Z","msg":"真係好噁心<br />\n口裡講到好愛我<br />\n但從來冇為我付出過<br />\n又勁計較又小氣<br />\n呢d我地一齊個時我都冇嘈過<br />\n最後一頂綠帽笠落我頭度<br />\n諗番真係覺得好噁心<br />\n又cheap人品又差<br />\n做錯事又唔認 仲將d責任推曬係我度<br />\n人又唔係醒目<br />\n英文係初中水平<br />\n樣又唔係靚仔<br />\n我當初接受佢純粹係以為佢唔識氹女仔<br />\n以為佢係純品好男仔 <br />\n但諗番同佢一齊過都覺得自己cheap左<br />\n好似踩過屎咁"},{"pid":"a4832ec76726104c6e6d28ba15dfce63530c6a48","tid":1788732,"uid":100016,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:12:01.000Z","msg":"主要係綠帽姐，拉。"},{"pid":"51be3f783de4fecf76516e219c1de882b246fb20","tid":1788732,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:12:31.000Z","msg":"一諗起佢壓落自己un個時？"},{"pid":"5632dac34bdfbecb937aa2f0cc62b9225581a261","tid":1788732,"uid":295958,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"a4832ec76726104c6e6d28ba15dfce63530c6a48","tid":1788732,"uid":100016,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:12:01.000Z","msg":"主要係綠帽姐，拉。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:13:27.000Z","msg":"係 當初佢話性格不合想分手個時<br />\n我除左傷心之外 都冇怨過<br />\n佢後尾先發現 佢話性格不合個時<br />\n其實佢已經現緊交友app flirt緊第二條女"},{"pid":"545debd14d81c6cf1deb72dce260bf85779423cb","tid":1788732,"uid":295958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51be3f783de4fecf76516e219c1de882b246fb20","tid":1788732,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:12:31.000Z","msg":"一諗起佢壓落自己un個時？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:13:52.000Z","msg":"拍得唔醜聞<br />\n所以冇發生過"},{"pid":"fdc44a145ba0ea5b01b132811769c206f5096989","tid":1788732,"uid":295958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"545debd14d81c6cf1deb72dce260bf8577942